title: Conti Ransomware Operator Extradited to the United States

content.raw: A Ukrainian national accused of participating in one of the most damaging ransomware campaigns in history has been extradited from Ireland to face charges in the United States. Oleksii Oleksiyovych Lytvynenko, 43, appeared in federal court in Tennessee following his transfer from Irish custody, where he had been held since his arrest in July 2023.
